        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffffff>「總共有五種。形態而言，對應的分別是禮冠、花、杯皿、時計與鳥羽。」</color>",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/29/142453215/007b2301e4bea556414efaeebc2ad288_4950923372101656552.png",
        "alignment": "left"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "聖遺物可以細分為五個部位： <color=#ffe14b>生之花</color> 、 <color=#ffe14b>死之羽</color> 、 <color=#ffe14b>時之沙</color> 、 <color=#ffe14b>空之杯</color> 、 <color=#ffe14b>理之冠</color>\n聖遺物也有星級之分（一星至五星）。不同星級的聖遺物也有對應的顏色區分：一星（灰色）、二星（青色）、三星（藍色）、四星（紫色）、五星（金色）。\n一星至五星的聖遺物均可以從等級0提升至各自的最大等級：一星（等級4）、二星（等級4）、三星（等級12）、四星（等級16）、五星（等級20）。\n聖遺物均可提高角色的屬性數值，稱為： <color=#ffffff>主要屬性</color> 、 <color=#ffffff>追加屬性</color> 。\n聖遺物主要屬性（主詞條）的數值會隨著等級的提升而固定提升；\n聖遺物追加屬性（副詞條）至多可以達到四個（不同星級的聖遺物均有不同）。\n不同的聖遺物也提供不同的套裝效果。\n以下是聖遺物五個部位的主要屬性："
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffffff>聖遺物部位</color>\n<color=#ffffff>主要屬性</color>\n<color=#ffe14b>生之花</color>\n生命值\n<color=#ffe14b>死之羽</color>\n攻擊力\n<color=#ffe14b>時之沙</color>\n攻擊力百分比\n防禦力百分比\n生命值百分比\n元素精通\n元素充能效率\n<color=#ffe14b>空之杯</color>\n攻擊力百分比\n防禦力百分比\n生命值百分比\n元素精通\n物理傷害加成\n元素傷害加成\n<color=#ffe14b>理之冠</color>\n攻擊力百分比\n防禦力百分比\n生命值百分比\n元素精通\n治療加成\n暴擊率\n暴擊傷害",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "以下是各個主要屬性在最大等級時的數值："
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffffff>星級</color>\n<color=#ffffff>（最大等級）</color>\n<color=#ffffff>五星</color>\n<color=#ffffff>（等級20）</color>\n<color=#ffffff>四星</color>\n<color=#ffffff>（等級16）</color>\n<color=#ffffff>三星</color>\n<color=#ffffff>（等級12）</color>\n<color=#ffffff>二星</color>\n<color=#ffffff>（等級4）</color>\n<color=#ffffff>一星</color>\n<color=#ffffff>（等級4）</color>\n<color=#ffffff>生命值</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>4780</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>3571</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>1893</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>551</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>324</color>\n<color=#ffffff>攻擊力</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>311</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>232</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>123</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>36</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>21</color>\n<color=#ffffff>攻擊力百分比</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>46.6%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>34.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>23.1%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>7.9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff>防禦力百分比</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>58.3%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>43.5%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>28.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>11.2%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>9.9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff>生命值百分比</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>46.6%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>34.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>23.1%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>7.9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff>元素精通</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>187</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>139</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>92</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>36</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>32</color>\n<color=#ffffff>元素充能效率</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>51.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>38.7%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>25.6%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>9.9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>8.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff>物理傷害加成</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>58.3%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>43.5%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>28.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>11.2%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>9.9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff>元素傷害加成</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>46.6%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>34.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>23.1%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>7.9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff>治療加成</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>35.9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>26.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>17.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>6.9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>6.1%</color>\n<color=#ffffff>暴擊率</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>31.1%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>23.2%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>15.4%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>6%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>5.3%</color>\n<color=#ffffff>暴擊傷害</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>62.2%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>46.4%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>30.8%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>11.9%</color>\n<color=#ffffff73>10.5%</color>",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/01/29/142453215/200c959851ea3abe3a535890f7202a63_7169513764288691377.png",
        "alignment": "left"
