        "desc": "<p>用黑色晶石精心雕琢而成的花朵，在夜間似乎會散發出神秘的幽光。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/08/23/cd11df3be5420d2c53c2da0d3298eb92_4238581052558034331.png",
        "displayStyle": "card",
